00:10:05.470 --> 00:10:08.300
to clamp the cell with a real

00:10:08.300 --> 00:10:10.760
honest to God action potential.

00:10:10.760 --> 00:10:12.750
We've of course not been able to do that,

00:10:12.750 --> 00:10:16.117
this is just simply an
electrical field stimulation.

00:10:16.117 --> 00:10:18.590
And it's absolutely possible

00:10:18.590 --> 00:10:22.530
that the shape of the action
potential will have an effect.

00:10:22.530 --> 00:10:25.310
Certainly the temperature
of an action potential

00:10:25.310 --> 00:10:26.845
