channels to open slowly.

00:10:30.630 --> 00:10:32.989
So, these are things that we know happen,

00:10:32.989 --> 00:10:35.700
and we're not able to
do that in our system,

00:10:35.700 --> 00:10:38.930
we really need to be able to
voltage clamp those cells,

00:10:38.930 --> 00:10:41.970
and then you can only do
that in the calyx of Held,

00:10:41.970 --> 00:10:44.450
